    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/5e23e33c7afe489979ae4fdb0a589ace.webp?t=1752183780\" width=800 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ezrebeth is an old, bitter recluse who finds herself constantly invaded by her peculiar relatives during the winter holidays. Oh, and she's stuck in a time loop! Investigate, interview and cross-reference as you attempt to figure out what's going on in this surreal visual novel.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This demo lets you experience the beginning of the first episode, roughly 30 minutes of playtime.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/b9fc975bb1df99babdd8f89be305fee6.webp?t=1752183780\" width=597 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/d3a2eb8de04f5a26a7c4e0c01bc167a4.webp?t=1752183780\" width=11 height=11 /></span> <strong>Enter</strong> a one-of-a-kind narrative full of domestic drama, light horror, witty puns and deep, resonating themes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/d3a2eb8de04f5a26a7c4e0c01bc167a4.webp?t=1752183780\" width=11 height=11 /></span> <strong>Meet</strong> the Casarecce family, a host of memorable characters to interview and/or interrogate as you uncover the truth behind the mysterious time loop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/d3a2eb8de04f5a26a7c4e0c01bc167a4.webp?t=1752183780\" width=11 height=11 /></span> <strong>Three</strong> games in one! Unlock two additional episodes after completing the main story, which further expand on the characters and the strange world they find themselves in (total playtime: 5-8 hours)! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/d3a2eb8de04f5a26a7c4e0c01bc167a4.webp?t=1752183780\" width=11 height=11 /></span> <strong>Beautiful</strong> and unique artwork drawn by hand, all available to view in a dedicated gallery of memories! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/d3a2eb8de04f5a26a7c4e0c01bc167a4.webp?t=1752183780\" width=11 height=11 /></span> <strong>Relax</strong> your mind to a melancholic soundtrack courtesy of professional musicians Crowander and Derek Clegg! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dedicated to the memory of Sven Johan Borgelind (1945-2022).</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/abda068d0269f2390b46bdf9a0da2470.webp?t=1752183780\" width=597 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/807121a081fe487e12b462fd9b6637fc.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/bd4918828869ac6b52c6ffae9cc8be14.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/d8263b579742ba275c2584f0b51397d3.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/db5cd86a6735bd64eb51a556ea40fb7f.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/08fa4a971c51128c67d6f75075908ae4.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/7d8ff04bdcf7a1f06e2590cc406a5de4.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/f75acfc5b28260c2da2b48d281e70752.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206570/extras/c8bef7d9d0248731d0b7583d8e7ea158.avif?t=1752183780\" width=550 height=250 /></span></p>",
